ingredients: ["1 1/2 c. self-rising cornmeal", "1 c. self-rising flour", "1 medium onion, chopped finely", "1 egg", "1 Tbsp. sugar", "1 c. milk"]
directions: ["Combine cornmeal, flour, onion and sugar.", "Add egg.", "Gradually beat in milk.", "Drop by spoonfuls into hot oil.", "I use a Fry Baby and fry 4 hush puppies at a time.", "They flip over when brown on one side.", "If you have more than needed, pop the remaining in a freezer bag and freeze.", "Just heat when needed."]
